freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: 50 minutes after injection. Wanted to sneeze once. Also my sinuses dried up with no leaking. 90 minutes later only about 15-20 seconds of very mild pain. Next day only pain when I press on injection site. Sleep good!

A bit of pulsing in my left tricep and left bicep. Might be just related to weight lifting. Also just now pain in my dinghy thump at and into base of right hand. May be due to topical steroid with drawls syndrome or poor dietetic measures today with not enough water intake.
Dont know if symptoms are vaccine related or using 4,000mg of L-HistaDine daily for other condition
Fast heart beat for a bit when sleeping
I think I ate too much and did not exercise enough yesterday
Very, very mild. Maybe not related
